## Engine & Variable Store — No Hardcoded Paths

**Rule:** `lib/sdui/sdui-engine.tsx` and `lib/sdui/global-variable-store.ts` must not hardcode domain-specific paths. All paths and defaults come from `config/store.json`.

**engineConventions (store.json):**

| Key | Purpose | Default |
|-----|---------|---------|
| `themePath` | Path to persist theme (setTheme action) | `nav.colorScheme` |
| `defaultPaginationPath` | Default path for goToPage (skip/offset) | `collectionSkip` |
| `defaultPaginationFetchAction` | Default fetch action for goToPage | `fetchCollection` |
| `shareSlugPrefix` | URL prefix when share url is a slug (e.g. `/product`) | `/product` |

**variableStoreInitial (store.json):** Drives initial state for the global variable store. Define paths that need initial values (e.g. `collectionSkip`, `sortMenuOpen`, `product.selectedOptions`). Never hardcode these in `global-variable-store.ts`.
